---
/**
 * EarthFeed.astro — v6.4 "Earth Mission Control" news-from-Earth ticker.
 *
 * Server-rendered horizontally scrolling tape carrying the 36-event news-
 * burst corpus. Mirrors the MarketTape CSS-only infinite-pan technique
 * (track duplicated for seamless loop, `translateX(-50%)` keyframes,
 * hover-pause, reduced-motion static fallback) but with calmer cadence —
 * 96s traversal vs MarketTape's 60s — because per-city news reads slower
 * than per-symbol quotes.
 *
 * Source corpus (36 events):
 *   - 4 Digos (home base) · 6 APAC × 2 events · 4 EMEA × 2 events ·
 *     4 Americas × 2 events
 *   - All NDA-positive. Generic language only — no employer / platform
 *     / proprietary-signal name in any string.
 *
 * Signal category → color (palette tokens):
 *   long-vol       → fail (red)
 *   short-vol      → pass (green)
 *   flatten        → accent-cyan
 *   steepen        → amber-light
 *   carry          → amber alpha (F14 institutional)
 *   breakeven-watch / regime-shift → ink-2 (neutral)
 *
 * Hard constraints honored:
 *   - No `client:*`, no `Math.random()`, no `Date.now()`.
 *   - Palette tokens only.
 *   - `prefers-reduced-motion: reduce` honored.
 */
import { path } from '@utils/url';

